|Ultrasonic Sensor|1|HC-SR04|"HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor"|₹80-150|
|LED (Green)|1|5mm|"5mm Green LED"|₹5-10|
|LED (Yellow)|1|5mm|"5mm Yellow LED"|₹5-10|
|LED (Red)|1|5mm|"5mm Red LED"|₹5-10|
|Resistors|3|220Ω|"220 Ohm Resistor Pack"|₹20-40|
