|LED (Red)|1|5mm|"5mm Red LED"|₹5-10|
|Buzzer|1|5V active buzzer|"5V Active Buzzer"|₹20-40|
|Resistors|2|220Ω (for LEDs)|"220 Ohm Resistor Pack"|₹20-40|
|Breadboard|1|400/830 points|"Breadboard 830 points"|₹80-150|
